WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love In A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.287
=Episode 7=

00:02:18.720 --> 00:02:20.720
(She's just like her mother!)

00:02:20.720 --> 00:02:21.920
(Both of them love drawing!)

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:34.280
(Of all the people to draw,
she just had to draw Man!)

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:36.160
(Is she seeking revenge on me?)

00:02:36.160 --> 00:02:38.720
(Is she seeking revenge on me
for stealing her father from her?)

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.320
(No way!)

00:02:40.320 --> 00:02:42.080
(Not Man!)

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:43.500
(I won't let her steal him from me!)

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:15.240
(What should we do?)

00:05:28.600 --> 00:05:31.320
I heard that you had a message for me.

00:05:31.320 --> 00:05:34.040
What's the matter, Young Master Chen?

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:35.600
What do you need?

00:05:35.920 --> 00:05:37.640
Jia.

00:05:37.640 --> 00:05:40.840
I know you've been doing well
in Hai City when I wasn't around.

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:44.640
You may choose to rob people,

00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:47.400
but there are certain people
you shouldn't offend.

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:48.560
What do you mean by that?

00:05:48.760 --> 00:05:52.400
I heard that you lost a race
you bet on a few days ago.

00:05:52.400 --> 00:05:54.320
And, you've been
inquiring about the girl.

00:05:54.680 --> 00:05:57.800
What's with that?
Are you trying to seek revenge here?

00:05:58.200 --> 00:06:01.120
Is she your girl?

00:06:03.350 --> 00:06:05.137
You don't look that dumb.

00:06:05.137 --> 00:06:05.937
Listen up.

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:07.482
You'd better stay away from her.

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:10.160
If you lost your bet, you can
get it back from other races.

00:06:10.400 --> 00:06:12.040
Don't be so narrow-minded.

00:06:12.837 --> 00:06:14.317
You shouldn't target her.

00:06:14.317 --> 00:06:16.597
I suppose I have to
show you some respect.

00:06:19.562 --> 00:06:20.362
Thanks.

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:37.280
The beef is pretty good.

00:06:59.880 --> 00:07:01.040
Zhu,

00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:02.800
Qingbai is treating you kindly.

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:04.400
You need to learn how to be respectful.

00:07:06.120 --> 00:07:08.560
Do you think everything you see

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:10.160
is real?

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:12.480
What do you mean?

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:13.520
I'm saying

00:07:15.880 --> 00:07:17.000
that she's keeping up an act.

00:07:17.312 --> 00:07:18.112
Lu Zhu.

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:21.400
Why are you getting
more and more unreasonable?

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:23.480
How could you change this drastically?

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:24.280
You...

00:07:26.700 --> 00:07:27.762
You're just being willful.

00:07:28.412 --> 00:07:29.692
What an insensible girl.

00:07:36.600 --> 00:07:37.480
Are you full?

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:41.680
Man,

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:42.760
what about this?

00:07:42.760 --> 00:07:43.520
You can take a walk

00:07:43.520 --> 00:07:44.720
in the garden with your mother.

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:46.760
It'll aid her digestion.

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:47.800
Okay.

00:07:48.640 --> 00:07:49.560
Let's go.

00:07:51.240 --> 00:07:52.040
Okay.

00:08:05.080 --> 00:08:06.200
Zhu.

00:08:06.880 --> 00:08:07.880
I know.

00:08:08.760 --> 00:08:11.760
You were never happy
with my second marriage.

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:15.400
But since it has come to this,
you should be sensible.

00:08:16.880 --> 00:08:19.800
I need a companion somehow.

00:08:20.640 --> 00:08:24.400
Besides, being together with Qingbai

00:08:24.700 --> 00:08:26.020
feels great.

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:29.760
I don't think so.

00:08:31.840 --> 00:08:33.520
What do you want, then?

00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:40.560
Zhu, from what I can remember,

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:42.800
you were always obedient
and sensible from a young age.

00:08:43.100 --> 00:08:44.500
You were kind and generous too.

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:47.520
It's been over a year
since you came back,

00:08:47.520 --> 00:08:49.160
and somehow it feels really strange.

00:08:49.900 --> 00:08:51.400
It's like I don't know you anymore.

00:08:51.400 --> 00:08:53.240
What exactly happened to you?

00:08:56.400 --> 00:08:57.200
Dad.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:09:01.100
You always wanted me to be
the good daughter of the Lu family.

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:04.280
That identity is constraining me
like a pair of shackles.

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:07.240
There's a template for the way I eat,

00:09:07.240 --> 00:09:08.560
the way I walk,

00:09:08.560 --> 00:09:11.640
even the way I speak.

00:09:12.600 --> 00:09:15.720
Do you want me to live like a doll
for my entire life?

00:09:16.920 --> 00:09:17.840
No.

00:09:18.160 --> 00:09:18.960
I don't want that.

00:09:18.960 --> 00:09:20.120
- I just hope that...
- Dad.

00:09:20.920 --> 00:09:24.480
I heard your deal with Mr. Shu
and the rest didn't go through.

00:09:25.760 --> 00:09:27.160
Why are you asking me that?

00:09:27.160 --> 00:09:29.520
If so, does that mean you won't
let Man join the company?

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:31.560
Why would you think of it that way?

00:09:34.280 --> 00:09:36.320
Why are you so kind to Huang Qingbai,

00:09:36.560 --> 00:09:38.120
yet so harsh to her son?

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:40.920
How could that be?

00:09:40.920 --> 00:09:43.120
I admire Man a lot.

00:09:43.937 --> 00:09:45.657
If so, you should let him
join the company.

00:09:47.787 --> 00:09:49.027
If you can do that,

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:52.440
I can accept the fact
that you love Huang Qingbai.

00:09:53.562 --> 00:09:54.882
But if you can't,

00:09:55.262 --> 00:09:57.062
that means you don't love her at all.

00:09:57.880 --> 00:09:59.360
Silly girl.

00:09:59.360 --> 00:10:01.160
These two are completely
different matters.

00:10:01.160 --> 00:10:02.760
How can I prove myself with that alone?

00:10:05.640 --> 00:10:07.880
Dad, it's because I want you

00:10:07.880 --> 00:10:10.440
to find a life companion
for the second half of your life

00:10:11.600 --> 00:10:13.400
rather than self-hypnosis.

00:10:13.400 --> 00:10:15.560
Even I think

00:10:16.625 --> 00:10:18.987
that Ms. Huang Qingbai

00:10:20.520 --> 00:10:22.440
resembles Mom too much.

00:10:27.500 --> 00:10:32.000
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:10:32.225 --> 00:10:36.013
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:10:36.188 --> 00:10:40.263
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:10:40.263 --> 00:10:44.400
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:10:44.525 --> 00:10:48.300
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:10:48.300 --> 00:10:52.075
♪I'll learn to stop
longing for what's gone♪

00:10:52.075 --> 00:10:54.350
♪The you in my memories♪

00:10:54.350 --> 00:10:56.363
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:10:56.363 --> 00:11:01.800
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:11:03.363 --> 00:11:08.800
♪Forget you completely♪